{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You're just here to do a job. The universe has other plans for you.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Planet Scanner is a semi-procedural horror narrative disguised as a job simulator set in an isolated, cramped space station.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are ScanCorp's newest Planet Scanner and your task is to discover, study, and claim distant planets on behalf of your employer. The business of selling planets is booming, especially as the search for intelligent alien life heats up...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>GET YOUR ASSIGNMENTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your computer to check emails, get your daily assignments, and learn more about the galaxy around you. Stay up to date with the news, check the market prices for certain planetary traits, and buy upgrades to make your job easier!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SCAN THE STARS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684360/extras/StoreGIF__1_.gif?t=1729615301\" />The telescope is your main way of observing the universe, so use it to lock onto a star and bring up its' local system on the map console. Scan planets to discover them, learn more about their unique properties, and upload them to ScanCorp's servers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SEARCH FOR SIGNALS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684360/extras/SignalGIF.gif?t=1729615301\" />You may be asked to ping planets in search of potential alien transmissions. Lock in the waveforms, decrypt the signals, and hopefully don't open a Pandora's box you never could have fathomed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">TAKE IMAGES OF PLANET SURFACES</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684360/extras/ImagerGIF.gif?t=1729615301\" />Sometimes, the only way to learn more about a planet is to take a look for yourself. Find a good imaging sight, match the coordinates, and see what lurks on the surface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Total playtime averages about 2.5 hours. There are 23 in-game nights.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Contact","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2684360/c55dad3666e2775acbe018bcffd3b97a76ec7c43.jpg"},{"name":"Let It In","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2684360/81eb9a6a26a27b70d01cab073bc0d4bafc43acc7.jpg"},{"name":"Planet Scanner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2684360/c682e2695997236104f30591588fcc09cce52119.jpg"},{"name":"Loyal Customer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2684360/692f461946f3ed9e8a785d39f79c1ae76007c172.jpg"},{"name":"Home.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2684360/c75341060a421266af9def85b8b5d70d5574bf3c.jpg"},{"name":"Signal Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2684360/e2d4c413137cd51dfaacca890f5ecae95f06464e.jpg"},{"name":"Star Child","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2684360/08c3b09e27d6139246857cda06681e9bcda0c146.jpg"},{"name":"Side Hustle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2684360/3f6d2cd7606853e1cc33771bcb728954a1e602cb.jpg"},{"name":"Terminated","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2684360/9709af2b65681e35353b7a988c925f8861d71e94.jpg"},{"name":"On Company Time","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamco